sellerCard.description:
I am an experienced WordPress Developer with 7 years of professional experience in the industry. I have a proven track record of success, with over 600 satisfied clients leaving 5-star reviews for my work. I have a deep understanding of WordPress and its ecosystem, including theme and plugin development, customization, and performance optimization.

LET'S DEVELOP A WEBSITE TOGETHER.

description.content:
Hi Everyone,


Looking for a fully responsive wordpress website ? Wordpress Blog? Wordpress Lead generating site ? You have found the right gig. Let me take over your head-ace.


I have over 5 years of experience working with wordpress and I can do awesome, responsive, professional & eye catching websites, e-commerce stores and blogs.


I can also modify your current website to make it look like how you want or I can also start from scratch depending up on whatever you wanna get done.


Below are the different services & addons that I offer for free..


Whats Special?

  • Royalty Free Images
  • Designing Services to some extend, which you wont get in development gig, but I offer that too.


Why Me ?

  • Over 5 years of experience
  • 300+ 5 star feedbacks
  • Deliver Luxury Websites
  • Over 250 clients satisfied
  • Woocommerce & Stores Expert
  • Gravity Form Expert
  • Elementor Expert
  • Shopify Expert
  • Beaver Builder Expert
  • Can work in any theme you buy


Note: The pricing can be somehow different according to the development requirement.


Feel free to get in touch with to ask anything that you feel is not mentioned in the gig or you have got any special requirements.


Please contact before placing order!

questionsAndAnswers.question: What details should i provide before starting
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
You will have to provide:
1. WordPress Admin Panel
2. Cpanel
3. The account login where I could manage your domain (if needed).

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Domain and Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, but if want I can provide you with some extra charges.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you have Portfolio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will Provide you my portfolio/sample sites before placing your order.

reviews.comment: Fawad is an exceptional talent when it comes to web design and everything related to websites. Our organization had an existing website built with Elementor on WordPress, and we needed revisions to both the content and design. Not only was Fawad patient throughout the process, but he also communicated effectively, ensuring that every issue we had was resolved. My team is beyond satisfied with his work, and we’ll absolutely be using him for future projects. I highly recommend and fully endorse the quality of his work. If you’re looking for a web designer who pays attention to detail and goes above and beyond to ensure you love the final product, look no further than Fawad. Honestly, if a 10-star rating existed, he’d have mine!

The website they created for me has malware.  It’s costing me hundreds of dollars to get this fixed and I’m losing so much money because my clients cannot access my website because of this issue. I attempted to give them the opportunity to remove the malware, but they did not seem very knowledgeable. Still insisting the website is safe, although I can’t even access it from my own computer because of my virus protection. In addition to several different companies, rejecting my emails because of the website issues.

I’m happy that i choosed Fawad to helping me creating my website, he went above and beyond to reach my expectations and he’s very professional and absolute expert in what he do. Thank you so much Fawad for your great effort and I will continue to use your services again in the future!

Fawad Ahmed developed a website that was exactly what we were looking for. His attention to detail and professionalism were second to none. He delivered within the timeframe he promised. I will definitely use Fawad's services for future projects. I will also recommend Fawad to others.

He is very skilled and he exceeded my expectations.
He delivered on time and with a very high quality.
I highly recommend his services and i will buy again from him.

reviews_snippet.comment:
Fawad delivers exceptional quality work and his professionalism is a joy to witness.

You can’t go wrong choosing him!

Fawad Ahmed did an OUTSTANDING job on our website development! His attention to detail and professionalism not only exceeded our expectations but made the whole journey smooth with proactive communication and excellent cooperation. Highly recommend working with him! 👍

Fawad is very knowledgeable, responsive, and on top of the revisions requested.  He is a pleasure to work with, will hire him again!
Thank you Fawad for always assisting us anytime we call. We come to Fawad anytime we may need assistance with our website.
